Steps to connect the sql-server with database

1::
data->from databases-> from sql server databases

2::
do the connection and the tables 
 3:: 
 go for the recent scources and connect your scource
 
 4:: will get all the tables from the databases click on edit
 
 5:: the power shell will open on the right side click on star like button
 
 6:: you will get the connection by default and on clicking advance setting you will the query editor
